{"tid":1743074,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"區選 ＝ 公投","createTime":"2019-11-21T05:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T06:48:51.000Z","uid":222614,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"cebee2294ac8674b6c02f6952d8ac775397cc18f","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"自六月以黎，特區政府同香港人一直打緊民意戰，依家正正係時候需要一種方式去將民意量化，將結果公之於世<br />\n<br />\n可惜香港並無公投法可以去量化民意，但好在有區選<br />\n今次區選嘅日期正正落係一個極佳嘅時候，令到佢變成一個量化民意嘅工具，取代公投<br />\n<br />\n而今次嘅公投議題就係：<br />\n投泛民 ＝ 光復香港，時代革命<br />\n投建制 ＝ 維護特區，以暴制亂<br />\n<br />\n當然，啲票畀左泛民唔等於佢地會聽香港人支笛（事實上泛民做啲咩唔做啲咩大家一向都控制唔到），但呢樣並唔係重點，最重要嘅係民意得到量化，確實咁展現係所有人面前<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家唔好將重點擺係泛民度，今次嘅重點係公投！"},{"pid":"7e77f563c82e489d8f16ac1664c32f8d94a8b0c5","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"公投！"},{"pid":"e586d758ae97c77a70780424b74b05fb760aa0cd","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"Suffrage Universel !"},{"pid":"5f237305ea9bf49add243ff0f1f226c48327375a","tid":1743074,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"區選諗住投白票/廢票嘅人不妨睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9de88d04ce48e46a040691aad598383276697477","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"Universal Suffrage!"},{"pid":"11877fdba8829bf1a574864c978897ca3e738ac2","tid":1743074,"uid":26424,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"輸咗點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d913361096fae032af7a72fb97197192f4dfc63","tid":1743074,"uid":47110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11877fdba8829bf1a574864c978897ca3e738ac2","tid":1743074,"uid":26424,"like