早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=ec40a52a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=94498e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=8b872ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=88420fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"7d633365461e28754b7e768afa1b6b7e9e9e9338","tid":1743074,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"359a73865e9d24c4bbc081090df2af44fdee7528","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955e35962553b827cb2d010eadc67a96a8ca4fa5","tid":1743074,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b85cd2301cc450036b7eee657143e4b2e4869a","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得會輸"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"贏左既話<br />\n跟住點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"揸住個結果，你想點用都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"嘩 你講到政府好聽民意咁"},{"pid":"07b8acfdf8f9b1c8f9988bf91631743fbe7237b3","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">量化民意</span>"},{"pid":"a6222b76574edc53af4cb7f29ef800c7aba1ce63","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955e35962553b827cb2d010eadc67a96a8ca4fa5","tid":1743074,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b85cd2301cc450036b7eee657143e4b2e4869a","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11877fdba8829bf1a574864c978897ca3e738ac2","tid":1743074,"uid":26424,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"輸咗點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得會輸"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"贏左既話<br />\n跟住點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啲人成日都驚輸民意，用民意黎綁手綁腳<br />\n<br />\n贏左嘅話即係仍然有民意支持繼續時代革命<br />\n如果大勝，即係表示行動有民意基礎，會變成日後行動既主要推動力</span>"},{"pid":"535700b613b40d520615c53c495ad6e8f7eecd9f","tid":1743074,"uid":28202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11877fdba8829bf1a574864c978897ca3e738ac2","tid":1743074,"uid":26424,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"輸咗點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"我認為將區議會=公投係好危險，係未泛民大敗等於抗爭輸咗<br />\n人口溝淡換血殖民殖咗廿年,仲有無64比都好懷疑,<br />\n而且仲種票,癲係上嚟換票箱都仲得<br />\n搵個咁唔可靠既選舉制度做公投,好危險"},{"pid":"1acaf9c055a22b96dc18ec67c3c2f957153974f7","tid":1743074,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"我諗真係搞一個公投會好d"},{"pid":"670c2c5cf5d4471d49cf3f9bccb1e02393806bb2","tid":1743074,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot